PrecisRe-appointment of PETER LUSZTIG, of Vancouver, British Columbia, as British Columbia Treaty Commissioner, as nominated by Canada, to hold office during pleasure, for a term of two years, effective April 14, 2001 and ending on the earlier of April 13, 2003, or the date on which the appointment is terminated by Canada.
